Опис вакансії
Requirements:— Can-do attitude — Excellent knowledge of Turkish language— Good knowledge of the English language would be a plus— Flexibility on working hours and days (work by shifts)We offer:— Long-term employment with 20 working-days paid annual leave — Medical insurance — Support from colleagues and automatization of time-consuming processes — Sport activities — Free corporate English lessonsResponsibilities:— Help customers with complaints and questions— Give customers information about our web site and sportsbook— Make calls to customers in difficult cases (Full training will be provided)GENEL NİTELİKLER
Telefonda iletişim ve ikna kabiliyeti gelişmiş,
Türkçe Diksiyonu düzgün, akıcı ve etkin konuşabilen ,
